{"tid":2056071,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個返伏工嘅經驗","createTime":"2020-06-08T12:02:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T18:12:04.000Z","uid":314579,"like":40,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"39f574d9b531d2428a4525a58e24cda557eadd87","tid":2056071,"uid":314579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T12:02:02.000Z","msg":"歡迎大家入嚟分享返伏工嘅經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我係呢到分享先。<br />\n皆因早前疫情關係，周圍揾工，諗住乜工都做下先，冇錢，就係炒散王applied呢份<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hR39VSh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhR39VSh.png&h=323a0e3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n份工就係打電話叫今年dser上黎聽升學講座。<br />\n好啦，applied完佢請左我，第一日返工淨係返4個鐘，頭兩個鐘training冇錢收都算，仲要頭3日試用期淨係計$45/hr。所以唔好見佢招聘寫$55-70/hr，都係呃人。<br />\n好啦，到真係開工，佢要我地係2個鐘內邀請到3個。哇大佬，點撚樣叫一個第一日返工嘅人成功約到人上黎。咁如無意外，我係真係約唔到。然後佢叫我早少少收工走人，點之返到屋企佢就wts炒左我，對話如下:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bv1vFsK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbv1vFsK.png&h=e8e7e08c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ysTRpUq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FysTRpUq.jpg&h=a760fdae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實係第一日返工之前已經向佢報一個星期更，所以佢話夠人手個下真係o撚左，所以先同佢駁下。而且有試用期3日嘅話，就算覺得我真係唔掂，唔係應該過左3日試用期先炒我？仲要係返工前個一個星期特登叫我上黎見工，填form個啲，真係嘥撚晒我啲時間。而且佢唔肯銀行轉帳比我，得個$90都要我山長水遠過黎攞。<br />\n我知實有人話我好on9，咁都比人呃到上黎返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但冇計，前嗰排真係窮。我開得呢個post都係唔想再有人apply呢份工，又唔想真係有dser比人呃上黎聽嘢<br />\n<br />\n間公司係佐敦周生生大廈3樓，咪撚去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76fb7b7b522dfc33b2c3d87eb5e198060ead4550","tid":2056071,"uid":130627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T12:06:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"be0bbdccf5f95e93edd3a622c003a71e2d0e14e5","tid":2056071,"uid":55458,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T12:09:55.000Z","msg":"你居然敢踢爆我倒我米？"},{"pid":"3fff87881748383443fedb2eaea8b2c306488b29","tid":2056071,"uid":314579,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"be0bbdccf5f95e93edd3a622c003a71e2d0e14e5","tid":2056071,"uid":55458,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T12:09:55.000Z","msg":"你居然敢踢爆我倒我米？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T12:15:06.000Z","msg":"唔撚比？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cce89431bf48c9ad058a047967e273bec6e3bb03","tid":2056071,"uid":117443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T12:17:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ab879c5034b6c314be5af986652f55ec5b600943","tid":2056071,"uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T12:21:31.000Z","msg":"垃圾公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b80aba113a67d2e6bc749b4224ebbcea1194a10d","tid":2056071,"uid":314579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ab879c5034b6c314be5af986652f55ec5b600943","tid":2056071,"uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T12:21:31.000Z","msg":"垃圾公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T12:23:46.000Z","msg":"真係，好撚嬲，睇佢幾時執笠，啲員工幾時失業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bef31e69e8c6c5a389f6d3df42afeb8d08f0513","tid":2056071,"uid":48987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T12:23:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a12a94a7ddbf665be43e6f67473862dce20e3b0b","tid":2056071,"uid":89240,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T12:25:26.000Z","msg":"廢人俾人炒咁又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔通養你係到hea咩"},{"pid":"f6b999473eb52a92144ed5ad2027bd1b93f8a6b7","tid":2056071,"uid":71433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T12:27:48.000Z","msg":"呢d公司明顯就係呃人買課程架啦"},{"pid":"a89d5f983ea34cf118df25a9